  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 79,
      "chapterTitle": "半百上学堂",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300105565_79_373-518",
          "range": "373-518",
          "rangeStart": 373,
          "rangeEnd": 518,
          "markText": "年龄从来不是问题。\n真希望这句话是真的。\n可老子早就说了，“信言不美，美言不信”，真话不中听，动听的肯定是骗人的。活到半百，重新背着书包上学去，要说年龄不是问题，大概只有鬼相信。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1721693176,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-07-23 08:06:16",
          "chapterUid": 79,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=79&rangeStart=373&rangeEnd=518",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=79&rangeStart=373&rangeEnd=518"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_77_2488-2553",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "2488-2553",
      "markText": "原来人生下半场还能这样—— 除了带娃，除了游山玩水，还可以背着书包上学堂。",
      "totalCount": 408,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=2488&rangeEnd=2553",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=2488&rangeEnd=2553"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_87_2877-2931",
      "chapterUid": 87,
      "range": "2877-2931",
      "markText": "在食堂啃无盐的玉米真是暴殄天物，一直觉得对不起玉米。忏悔几次之后我就决定买回宿舍蘸盐吃，不负佳人也不负肠胃。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=87&rangeStart=2877&rangeEnd=2931",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=87&rangeStart=2877&rangeEnd=2931"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_115_3708-3783",
      "chapterUid": 115,
      "range": "3708-3783",
      "markText": "为什么爱看书？书中自有一个迥异于现实的世界，穿越文字，宛若与丑陋的现实暂时隔断，来到世外桃源。而且最妙的是，好书永远读不完，静好的桃源永远找得到入口。",
      "totalCount": 299,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=115&rangeStart=3708&rangeEnd=3783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=115&rangeStart=3708&rangeEnd=3783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_126_3419-3447",
      "chapterUid": 126,
      "range": "3419-3447",
      "markText": "依我的经验，结婚穿什么都一样，不穿红鞋，照样有火坑等着。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=126&rangeStart=3419&rangeEnd=3447",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=126&rangeStart=3419&rangeEnd=3447"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_77_1445-1480",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "1445-1480",
      "markText": "两年后重考，赶紧办退休。八月一日退休生效，八月三十一日就飞到北大报到。",
      "totalCount": 255,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=1445&rangeEnd=1480",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=1445&rangeEnd=1480"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_80_2334-2411",
      "chapterUid": 80,
      "range": "2334-2411",
      "markText": "幸好台湾阿姨颇能自我安慰：笨鸟慢飞嘛！更何况，我很早就发现，这一生，我的生命动线始终都是低开高走，起头少有顺遂的，可一段时间过后，便如倒吃甘蔗，渐入佳境。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=80&rangeStart=2334&rangeEnd=2411",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=80&rangeStart=2334&rangeEnd=2411"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_77_2366-2416",
      "chapterUid": 77,
      "range": "2366-2416",
      "markText": "终有一天，我也会闭上眼睛，关停所有的感官，任令亲人对着大体垂泪，却无能做出任何有形式、有意义的回应。",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=77&rangeStart=2366&rangeEnd=2416",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=77&rangeStart=2366&rangeEnd=2416"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_87_4793-4844",
      "chapterUid": 87,
      "range": "4793-4844",
      "markText": "即使在北京待了许久，每次听室友说体重几斤几斤的，还是挺不习惯。在台湾省，只有到市场买猪肉才这样说哩……",
      "totalCount": 224,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=87&rangeStart=4793&rangeEnd=4844",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=87&rangeStart=4793&rangeEnd=4844"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_112_2922-2972",
      "chapterUid": 112,
      "range": "2922-2972",
      "markText": "这就是人生。当下以为大不幸的事，一番转折之后，赫然发现竟是上天的眷顾。彻底的陈腔滥调，偏是真实不虚。",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=112&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2972",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=112&rangeStart=2922&rangeEnd=2972"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_118_2394-2415",
      "chapterUid": 118,
      "range": "2394-2415",
      "markText": "无有实力终无法立足。吃食如是，学问亦如是。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=118&rangeStart=2394&rangeEnd=2415",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=118&rangeStart=2394&rangeEnd=2415"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_109_3540-3567",
      "chapterUid": 109,
      "range": "3540-3567",
      "markText": "真正的“幸福”，是健康地活着，安详地死去，那才叫幸福！",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300105565&chapterUid=109&rangeStart=3540&rangeEnd=3567",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/42b32b40813ab8fbcg01551c?chapterUid=109&rangeStart=3540&rangeEnd=3567"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300105565_149_4231-4261",
